-- Brazil Ethanol Mills to Be Overseen by Oil Regulator ANP
-- B y   L u c i a   K a s s a i
-- 2012-08-31T11:44:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-31/brazil-ethanol-mills-to-be-overseen-by-oil-regulator-anp.html
Brazilian ethanol mills will be
overseen by the country’s ANP petroleum regulator, according to
a decree published in the government’s official gazette today.  The ANP will regulate the construction and expansion of
ethanol mills and the fuel’s production, according to the
decree.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lucia Kassai in Sao Paulo at 
 lkassai@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
